Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.07,0:01:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,史黛拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.86,0:01:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.62,0:01:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,臉色看起來比剛才好一點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.97,0:01:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你眼花了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.42,0:01:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,過來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.87,0:02:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,還沒死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.70,0:02:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.82,0:02:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,約瑟夫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.23,0:02:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,上次相見還是在墓地那裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.45,0:02:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,做得實在太過火了我想忘都忘不掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.28,0:02:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,他不記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.11,0:02:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,真是盡多管閒事啊…你這人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.06,0:02:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,算了 你也同意交易了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.54,0:02:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你和我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.16,0:02:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,一樣承受著強力的詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.98,0:02:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我受的是求死不能的詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.92,0:03:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你受的是求生不得的詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.80,0:03:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,所以把你的左手給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.85,0:03:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要的是我的左手？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.47,0:03:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.55,0:03:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,現在看起來這個是最有用的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.12,0:03:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,作為代價 我也給你自己身體的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.03,0:03:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣你也會變成不死之身了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.83,0:03:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我無法相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.29,0:03:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,難道你還有其他選擇嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.20,0:03:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你會給的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.96,0:03:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,把這條手臂給你就可以了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.43,0:03:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,在此之前 我們先確認下會不會有排異反應
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.05,0:04:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好 接下來輪到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.13,0:04:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 你還是怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.16,0:04:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,或許能將你從詛咒中解放出來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.47,0:04:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.10,0:04:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你也不會變成別的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.68,0:04:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,即使真的變了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.76,0:04:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.14,0:04:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你為何這麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.80,0:04:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.74,0:04:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.10,0:04:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我果然還是討厭你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.72,0:04:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我來幫你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.72,0:05:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.55,0:05:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,移植結束
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.09,0:05:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,別擔心 出這點血死不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.11,0:05:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,看來好像沒有排異反應
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.92,0:05:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你的眼球讓這世界看起來都閃閃發光了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.63,0:05:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好羨慕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.63,0:05:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我們是這個世上僅有的能看到相同東西的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.33,0:05:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,待你與詛咒融合後 我就拿走你那條手臂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.21,0:05:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,放心 在你醒來之前就全都能搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.09,0:05:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,借用一下你留在眼睛裡的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.79,0:05:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你要做什…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.23,0:05:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我說過了啊 我討厭你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.51,0:06:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,所以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.78,0:06:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,這是哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.38,0:06:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不認識啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.98,0:06:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不對…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.61,0:06:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,令人懷念…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.67,0:06:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我認得…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.72,0:06:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉哦 智世
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.27,0:06:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽…？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.48,0:06:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.49,0:06:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你看家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.32,0:06:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,害怕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.01,0:06:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不怕 和史輝在一起我一點都不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.19,0:06:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.12,0:06:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,史輝像爸爸一樣真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.10,0:06:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,這是在爸爸和弟弟消失前…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.26,0:06:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,史輝是個好孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我現在能給他換尿布了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.71,0:07:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,還真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.19,0:07:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.44,0:07:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,智世也是個好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.84,0:07:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.19,0:07:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我也來幫忙做飯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.49,0:07:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那讓你做些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我都能做
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.47,0:07:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,對的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.08,0:07:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,她曾是能露出那樣的表情 笑得那麼開心的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.07,0:07:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.06,0:07:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我淋濕了 你等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.14,0:07:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來 夕輝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.17,0:07:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,今天真晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.09,0:07:48.11,Default,背景,0,0,0,,{\an8}快點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.45,0:07:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了 智世
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.91,0:07:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.25,0:07:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 走不了路啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.78,0:08:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我以前是像爸爸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.85,0:08:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,工作太累了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.83,0:08:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,最近夜班變多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.93,0:08:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 要是我也能工作就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.15,0:08:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,智花在忙家事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.16,0:08:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,而且智世和智花一樣 這體質很麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.70,0:08:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,有你在她身邊我也就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.88,0:08:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你 夕輝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.97,0:08:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,體質…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.88,0:08:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽和我一樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.03,0:09:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,這是我的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.10,0:09:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他為了不讓我醒來 便讓我墜入這樣的夢中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.36,0:09:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,卡…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.00,0:09:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.26,0:09:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.70,0:09:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我是由他分離出來的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.56,0:09:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,他身上附著的各種東西都被他據為己有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.35,0:09:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,真正的他到底是怎麼樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.86,0:09:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,原本自己到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.03,0:09:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他已經不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.29,0:10:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼讓我看這些陳年往事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.05,0:10:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,大概是惡作劇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.90,0:10:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,那雖然在傷害你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.90,0:10:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,可也在保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.66,0:10:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你能和我這樣的東西說話也是拜其所賜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.02,0:10:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.08,0:10:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你最好別碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.43,0:10:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,在下定決心之前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.00,0:10:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,決心？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.00,0:10:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我來讓他靜一靜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.84,0:10:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.02,0:11:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 你要去哪兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.29,0:11:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,智世你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.99,0:11:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我很快回來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.20,0:11:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你等著哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.41,0:11:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.94,0:11:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,一路順風
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.80,0:11:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那之後爸爸再也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.69,0:11:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.80,0:11:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,沒回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.75,0:11:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你的記憶就到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.57,0:11:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,所以這扇門是不會開的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.34,0:11:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,夕輝？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.94,0:11:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.82,0:11:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,從這天開始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.12,0:12:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎麼…又這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.71,0:12:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.76,0:12:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,最近真是奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.10,0:12:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,羽鳥小姐來之後就這樣了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.59,0:12:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,要幫忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎回…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.54,0:12:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.57,0:12:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽明明說過不能害怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.37,0:12:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.28,0:12:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.49,0:12:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒事…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.75,0:12:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒事…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.44,0:12:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒事…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.27,0:13:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,救救我！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.13,0:13:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,救救我 媽媽！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.94,0:13:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,滾出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.63,0:13:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,快！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.39,0:13:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,大半夜的不能消停點嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.91,0:13:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定要保護她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.73,0:13:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定要保護她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.51,0:13:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定要振作起來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.52,0:13:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,最近那個一直保護她們的男人不見了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.82,0:13:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,真可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.17,0:13:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,他一定煩了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.90,0:13:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,被拋棄的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.31,0:13:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,被拋棄的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.49,0:13:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,可悲又美味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.03,0:14:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.80,0:14:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.72,0:14:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.54,0:14:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我一定要保護那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.82,0:14:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.15,0:14:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.77,0:14:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我一個人也可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.42,0:14:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.73,0:14:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,若沒有那孩子我就能解脫了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.54,0:14:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,沒這回事 不是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.32,0:15:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 只要那孩子不在…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.57,0:15:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我要是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.96,0:15:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,沒生下你就好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.05,0:15:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我要是沒生下你就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.88,0:15:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,媽…媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.91,0:16:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我做了什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.94,0:16:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.28,0:16:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 智世
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.10,0:16:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,原諒我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.96,0:16:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,惡作劇？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.08,0:16:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,這惡作劇…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.30,0:16:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,這惡作劇真夠惡意的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.06,0:16:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.52,0:16:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我要是沒生下你就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.78,0:17:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,都怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.17,0:17:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,都是因為你這體質
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.40,0:17:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.64,0:17:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.53,0:17:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你死了就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.75,0:17:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,去死去死去死去死去死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.30,0:17:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,去死去死去死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.24,0:17:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,去死！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.64,0:17:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,那為什麼最後沒有下手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.46,0:17:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是我真正的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.39,0:17:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你是我心裡的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.42,0:17:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,被媽媽掐著脖子的我創造出來的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.42,0:17:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,奈賓的話著實讓我收穫良多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.21,0:17:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,安潔莉卡小姐 賽門先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.15,0:17:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,愛麗絲他們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.08,0:17:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,林德爾先生和妖精之國的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.01,0:18:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,路茲 希露琪 史黛拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.16,0:18:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,艾利亞斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.36,0:18:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我很開心能遇到各種各樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.40,0:18:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,要不是這樣 我肯定在和你見面之前就死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.46,0:18:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,原諒我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.73,0:18:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,原諒我 智世
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.57,0:18:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,原諒我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.03,0:18:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽你也為我努力過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.41,0:18:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你一直在努力 但最後…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.97,0:18:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你是自由的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.03,0:18:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會原諒你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.68,0:18:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我很喜歡媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.38,0:19:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,和媽媽有過很多開心的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.20,0:19:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,但從那天起 我一點都想不起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.08,0:19:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但多虧了媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.15,0:19:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我遇到了一個喜歡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.78,0:19:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我在乎他超過我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.51,0:19:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我以為他很靠得住 但其實很讓人頭疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.54,0:19:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.87,0:19:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,所以啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.44,0:19:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你那天 鬆開了那雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.55,0:19:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然我不會原諒你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.23,0:19:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然我還不會忘記你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.46,0:19:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,但我會放下你 繼續前進
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.40,0:20:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,下定決心了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.67,0:20:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.02,0:20:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.03,0:20:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我是長生者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.79,0:20:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,為他而被賜予的詛咒和祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.95,0:20:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,約瑟夫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.64,0:20:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,卡塔菲爾斯的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.28,0:20:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,他們在你體內種下我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.55,0:20:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你準備接受我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.72,0:20:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,所以只要你想活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.22,0:20:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我就會成為你的祝福
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.46,0:20:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,即便要與侵蝕卻又保護著你的野獸撕咬不休
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.43,0:21:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.92,0:21:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你有什麼願望？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.30,0:21:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.60,0:21:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,代價是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.23,0:21:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,這事聽起來於我百利而無一害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.76,0:21:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,有一個我聽過很多次的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.42,0:21:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你能實現它嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.28,0:21:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,快要融合了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.17,0:21:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,真醜陋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.56,0:21:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,和我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.45,0:21:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你 你醒了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.40,0:21:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我也要學你的做法了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.51,0:21:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道能否實現
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.69,0:21:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你但說無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.26,0:21:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我來想辦法實現
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.48,0:21:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,救我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.47,0:21:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,救我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.16,0:21:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,救我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.83,0:22:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,救我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.35,0:22:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,數百年 數千年
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.65,0:22:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他們一直這樣吶喊著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.32,0:22:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道你們為何如此期望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.30,0:22:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,既有此念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.77,0:22:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,卻又為何要做這些事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.16,0:22:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,為何做了這些事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.21,0:22:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我要找出答案！
